{{Infobox language |name=Kofei |nativename= |region=[[Indonesia]]n [[Papua (Indonesian province)|Papua]] |speakers=100 |date=2000 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Papuan |fam1=[[East Geelvink Bay languages|East Geelvink Bay]]? |fam2= |iso3=kpi |glotto=kofe1239 |glottorefname=Kofei }} '''Kofei''' is a [[Papuan languages|Papuan language]] of the [[Indonesia]]n province of [[Papua (province)|Papua]], on the eastern shore of [[Cenderawasih Bay]].
Kofei is lexically similar to the [[East Geelvink Bay languages]] and presumably belongs in that family, but is too poorly attested to be sure.
